  "critical": false,
  "description": "Continuous iron smelting in tall shaft furnaces producing liquid pig iron (~4% C, ~1% Si) at 1200-1500°C. Cupola furnace remelts pig iron for casting. Three cast iron types: gray (excellent castability, machinable), white (hard, wear-resistant), malleable (heat-treated white iron, tougher). Produces 10-1000+ tonnes per day versus 5-20 kg per bloomery cycle.",
